column1: Pregnancies by age of woman (live/still births and induced abortions) (Annual-Dec)
Births exclude late registrations under section 16 of the Births, Deaths, Marriages, and Relationships Registration Act 1995.
Pregnancies include live births, stillbirths and induced abortions. These figures do not include miscarriages.
Live births and stillbirths included in the number of pregnancies for 1998 are based on birth notifications (not registrations).
Data has been randomly rounded to three to protect confidentiality. Individual figures may not add up to totals, and values for the same data may vary in different tables.
